<div id="Ch1.S3.SS8.p9" class="ltx_para">
<p id="Ch1.S3.SS8.p9.1" class="ltx_p">In summary: We have shown how to translate a condition about the
relative primality of two integers into a rather different condition which
has to do with representing integers as sums.</p>
</div>
